summary: During the 2019/2020 premier league season , west ham united sells the least expensive seasonal ticket at 320 British pounds , followed by manchester city for 325 British pounds . Every team 's seasonal cards ranged in pricing , some more than others , as for example tottenham 's cheapest season ticket cost 795 British pounds , their most expensive season ticket would cost 1,995 British pounds , which is still over 200 billion British pounds on the previous season , yet still represents the most expensive season ticket pricing in the premier league . Match-day tickets When it comes to match-day ticket prices , clubs show a slightly lower lower range .
gold: This graph depicts the top golf players in the official world ranking as of February 2020 , by average points . Top of the list was the British golfer , Rory McIlroy , who had an average of 9.48 points as of February 2020 .
